      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Aircraft Frame Structures are the structural components of an aircraft that provide support and stability.&lt;SEP&gt;Aircraft frame structures are the subject of non-destructive testing using acoustic emission analysis.</data>
