    <node id="Blind Source Separation">
      <data key="d0">Blind Source Separation</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Blind Source Separation is a technique used to separate multiple sources of acoustic emissions.&lt;SEP&gt;Blind source separation is a technique used to separate and characterize signal components when the signals from various sources and the mode of mixing are unknown.</data>
