      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">Tshilidzi Marwala is a researcher who co-authored the paper on the Bayesian Approach to Rough Set.&lt;SEP&gt;Author of the research paper&lt;SEP&gt;Tshilidzi Marwala is an author of the paper "A Study in a Hybrid Centralised-Swarm Agent Community".&lt;SEP&gt;Tshilidzi Marwala is a researcher involved in optimizing rough set partition sizes for HIV data analysis.&lt;SEP&gt;Tshilidzi Marwala is the third author of the study.&lt;SEP&gt;Co-author of the paper "Evolving Classifiers: Methods for Incremental Learning".</data>
