    <node id="Subset-Sum Problem">
      <data key="d0">Subset-Sum Problem</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">The Subset-Sum Problem is an NP-complete problem in computer science, where we need to find a subset of elements from a given set that sums up to a target value.</data>
